ZH: 他们之间的关系依然如故。
EN: Their relationship remains the same.

ZH: 虽然经历了种种变故，但他的信念依然如故。
EN: Despite all the changes, his beliefs stay the same.

ZH: 尽管时间已经过去很长，但他的承诺依然如故。
EN: Despite the passage of time, his promises remain unchanged.

ZH: 虽然环境在不断变化，但我们的目标依然如故。
EN: Despite the changing environment, our goals remain the same.

ZH: 尽管历经风雨，他的心态依然如故。
EN: Despite the hardships, his mindset remains unchanged.

ZH: 那片土地的风景依然如故，美丽而宁静。
EN: The scenery of that land remains the same, beautiful and peaceful.

ZH: 尽管生活有变化，我们的友谊依然如故。
EN: Despite the changes in life, our friendship remains the same.

ZH: 尽管他们曾分开一段时间，但他们的情感依然如故。
EN: Despite being apart for a while, their feelings remain the same.

ZH: 家乡的街道依然如故，仿佛时间停滞了。
EN: The streets of the hometown remain unchanged, as if time stood still.

ZH: 尽管对未来充满未知，他的决心依然如故。
EN: Despite the unknown future, his determination remains the same.

ZH: 尽管岁月已过，她的容颜依然如故。
EN: Despite the years that have passed, her beauty remains the same.

ZH: 即便有人变心，我的爱心依然如故。
EN: Even if someone changes their mind, my love remains the same.

ZH: 尽管外表变化，内心依然如故。
EN: Despite the outward changes, the inner self remains the same.

ZH: 尽管困难重重，她依然如故地坚持下去。
EN: Despite the many difficulties, she continues to persist as usual.

ZH: 尽管遭遇了挫折，他依然如故地保持乐观。
EN: Despite encountering setbacks, he remains optimistic as usual.

ZH: 尽管种种不顺，但他依然如故。
EN: Despite all the troubles, he remains the same.

ZH: 尽管时光流逝，但他们之间的默契依然如故。
EN: Despite the passing of time, their tacit understanding remains the same.

ZH: 尽管经历了磨难，她的心依然如故地善良如初。
EN: Despite the hardships, her heart remains kind as it was before.

ZH: 尽管遇到了困难，我们的团队依然如故地团结一致。
EN: Despite facing challenges, our team remains united as usual.

ZH: 尽管失去了很多，但他的信念依然如故。
EN: Despite losing a lot, his beliefs remain the same.
